\page page_2 Installation

Installation can currently only
be done on an ad-hoc basis. This document currently assumes that
installation has already been done by the application's author. 

The application has been compiled
for Windows and Linux environments.

\page page_3 Quick-start Guide

\section starting Starting ZZALOG</H2>
On Windows, ZZALOG may be started
by double clicking on the icon. It may also be started from a
terminal by advanced users.
On starting, a banner window is
displayed:
