&ldquo;QSL&rdquo;
- Displays the QSL status for this QSO &ndash; including displaying
any card image.
&ldquo;Contest&rdquo;
- Is used for contest operating.
&ldquo;Controls&rdquo;
- Displays all the operations available in the current state.
&ldquo;Rigs&rdquo;
- Displays the status of any connected rigs.
&ldquo;Clocks&rdquo;
- Displays the time in UTC (GMT or Zulu) and local time.
&ldquo;Log&rdquo;
- Displays the current status of the file.
&ldquo;QSLs&rdquo;
- Allows the control of data exchange with on-line QSL services.
&ldquo;Apps&rdquo;
- Provides control of other applications such as digital modems.
&ldquo;WX&rdquo;
- Displays the local weather obtained from openweather.org.
&ldquo;Bandplan&rdquo;
- Displays the local bandplan information.
